WEBVTT

00:00:59.461 --> 00:01:01.736
and public transit,

00:01:01.760 --> 00:01:04.188
but that does not define me.

00:01:04.553 --> 00:01:08.378
Each of us are different
and unique in our own way.

00:01:09.252 --> 00:01:12.839
However, there is not
a lot of information out there

00:01:12.863 --> 00:01:16.069
on what an autistic life
actually looks like,

00:01:16.093 --> 00:01:19.458
so people often resort to stereotypes.

00:01:19.831 --> 00:01:22.231
And we see these often in the media.

00:01:22.712 --> 00:01:26.744
Some of the more common
stereotypes in the media

00:01:26.768 --> 00:01:28.910
include being socially awkward,

00:01:28.934 --> 00:01:30.633
lacking empathy